                     Trance, Uplifting Trance | Armada Music

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-12-06 | 04:35:03 | 630 Mb


Based on A State of Trance, the weekly radio show of Armin van Buuren, one of the longest running shows in EDM, is the Future Favorite phenomenon. Each week, the over 20 million listeners have the chance to vote for their favourite tune, with the Future Favorite presented the week after. For all fans of the show, Armin now made a selection of Future Favourite picks, coming together on the 'Best of 2013' compilation. Including tunes by Andain, Solarstone, Dash Berlin, Ahmed Romel, W&W, Alexandre Bergheau, Wach, Aly & Fila, Alex M.O.R.P.H., Afternova and many more!
